ia Inquirer, and then went more deeply into the issues in a book, Temples o=
f Chance: How America Inc. Bought Out Murder Inc. to Win Control of the Cas=
ino Business. In all, I=92ve covered Donald Trump off and on for 27 years, =
and in that time I=92ve encountered multiple threads linking Trump to organ=
ized crime. Some of Trump=92s unsavory connections have been followed by in=
vestigators and substantiated in court; some haven=92t. And some of those l=
inks have continued until recent years, though when confronted with evidenc=
