l 27 phone call to respond to my questions for this story, Trump told me he=
 did not recall many of the events recounted in this article and they =93we=
re a long time ago.=94 He also said that I had =93sometimes been fair, some=
times not=94 in writing about him, adding =93if I don=92t like what you wri=
te, I=92ll sue you.=94Why did Trump get his casino license anyway? Why didn=
=92t investigators look any harder? And how deep did his connections to cri=
minals really go?

